pokedexEntries.gold: Its body can't be harmed by any sort of attack, so it is very eager to make challenges against enemies.
pokedexEntries.silver: Extremely strong, it can change the landscape. It has an insolent nature that makes it not care about others.
pokedexEntries.crystal: In just one of its mighty hands, it has the power to make the ground shake and mountains crumble.
pokedexEntries.ruby: Tyranitar is so overwhelmingly powerful, it can bring down a whole mountain to make its nest. This Pokémon wanders about in mountains seeking new opponents to fight.

pokedexEntries.fireRed: It has an impudent nature. Having great strength, it can even change surrounding landforms.
